  "description": "Mid-Range HEPA Air Purifier Comparative Research ¶Technical Specifications for 200-400 sq ft, $80-120 Market Segment Research Date: April 4, 2026\nScope: Verified specifications from manufacturer datasheets, AHAM Verified directory, Energy Star databases, and independent testing\nMethodology: Web research prioritizing primary sources (manufacturer sites, AHAM database, Energy Star listings) over marketing claims\n¶Executive Summary This research covers five primary models and identifies two additional strong competitors in the mid-range HEPA air purifier market. All five primary models are AHAM Verified with published CADR ratings. Price analysis shows most units cluster around 100−150retail,withfilterreplacementcostsrangingfrom100-150 retail, with filter replacement costs ranging from 20-50 depending on filter type and vendor.\n",
